graph TD
    User[User/External System] --> SupervisorAgent
    SupervisorAgent --> AgentRegistry
    SupervisorAgent --> AgentA[Agent A]
    SupervisorAgent --> AgentB[Agent B]

    AgentA --> SupervisorAgent
    AgentB --> SupervisorAgent

    SupervisorAgent -- delegates task --> AgentA
    SupervisorAgent -- delegates task --> AgentB

    AgentA -- requests tool --> ToolRegistry
    AgentB -- requests tool --> ToolRegistry

    ToolRegistry -- provides tool --> AgentA
    ToolRegistry -- provides tool --> AgentB

    AgentA -- executes tool --> ExternalTool[External Tool/Service]
    AgentB -- executes tool --> ExternalTool

    ExternalTool --> AgentA
    ExternalTool --> AgentB

    AgentA -- reports result --> SupervisorAgent
    AgentB -- reports result --> SupervisorAgent

    SupervisorAgent -- provides response --> User
